          </section>

          <p class="article-copy">Taking both of these charts together now, we can see for example that the most expensive section of the Artemis II SLS was the Core Stage, and that the Core Stage was designed and fabricated primarily by Boeing. Boeing has been at the heart of NASA’s spaceflight enterprise, having a hand in basically all of its missions since the initial 20th century Space Race.</p>
